Package io.crums.sldg

Class BaggedRow

java.lang.Object
io.crums.sldg.Row
io.crums.sldg.BaggedRow
All Implemented Interfaces:
io.crums.util.hash.Digest
public class BaggedRow
extends Row
Row backed by data in a RowBag. This is a departure (loosening up) from previous guarantees. Oh well, it's convenient, plus other classes like Path validate data on construction, besides.
